>\n香港理工大學 PolyU<br />\n香港教育大學 EdUHK<br />\n嶺南大學 LU<br />\n香港浸會大學 HKBU<br />\n香港城市大學 CityU<br />\n<br />\n香港演藝學院 HKAPA<br />\n<br />\n香港公開大學 OUHK<br />\n<br />\n香港樹仁大學 SYU<br />\n東華學院 Tung Wah College<br />\n珠海學院 Chu Hai College<br />\n明愛專上學院 Caritas Institute of Higher Education<br />\n香港能仁專上學院 Hong Kong Nang Yan College of Higher Education<br />\n恒生管理學院 HSMC<br />\n明德學院 Centennial College<br />\n宏恩基督教學院 Gratia Christian College<br />\n港專學院 HKCT<br />\n職業訓練局 - 香港高等教育科技學院 THEi"},{"pid":"be3d37cdab41e1703a3abbeff09cc1c6eb91c5d3","tid":519239,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:46:33.000Z","msg":"港大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5ff66875a6dd4593cc97047cc3c27bc889621f","tid":519239,"uid":53728,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"問題唔喺港大度<br />\n<br />\n問題係喺香港度"},{"pid":"fae7887d6e6f8df72fd1a1895d2977fc52b87ac0","tid":519239,"uid":114027,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"aa5ff66875a6dd4593cc97047cc3c27bc889621f","tid":519239,"uid":53728,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"問題唔喺港大度<br />\n<br />\n問題係喺香港度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"一來啦，二來佢根本從來都冇幫學校學生做過d咩<br />\n有咩議題就淨係識避，冇膊頭冇承擔，<br />\n咁的人唔配做港大校長"},{"pid":"a30c53eac8193f75d5ea81ed4dd44ddc1206cf27","tid":519239,"uid":53728,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問題唔喺港大度<br />\n<br />\n問題係喺香港度</blockquote>一來啦，二來佢根本從來都冇幫學校學生做過d咩<br />\n有咩議題就淨係識避，冇膊頭冇承擔，<br />\n咁的人唔配做港大校長</blockquote><br />\n認同馬斐森做唔到嘢<br />\n但馬斐森嗰屆亦係最難做嘅一屆<br />\n上屆徐立之因為李克強事件而請辭<br />\n政治干預開始滲透港大<br />\n馬斐森呢屆仲要撞正佔中<br />\n我係馬斐森我都揾退路走"},{"pid":"54e6d663aab88e7dc4d557e973b8b896866903b8","tid":519239,"uid":7375,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe4400cc10867f5cd59b4adbdec83f